Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
getVersion(25.10)                                            getVersion(25.10)

Name
       getVersion - Returns the Innovus software version number

Syntax
       getVersion

       [-help]

       [-major]

       Returns the Innovus software version number.

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description of the command.

              For a detailed description of the command, use the man command:

              man getVersion

       -major Returns the major version and one digit after the decimal point.

              Data_type: bool, optional

Examples
              * The following command returns the software version:

                innovus 7> getVersion

                20.10-d251_1

              * The following command gives the major version of the software:

                innovus 8> getVersion -major

                20.1

